<br />
Do you enjoy eating chocolate? just imagine if your government outlawed them. Assuming that you enjoy the odd chocolate bar. How would you feel that this happened when you can obviously control your habit? Just because the government decided that the a small fraction of the population cant stop stuffing them down, so they need to ban them all.<br />
