	<p>Ok, this law is ridiculous in many ways, but I only need to point out one of them.  How the hell are they going to enforce this law?<br />
<br />
That's right, there IS no way to completely enforce it.  Computers are everywhere, phones are sold with games installed on them (snake etc), most PC's are sold with games on them (solitaire etc.).<br />
<br />
There is no way they can enforce such a ridiculous law without the total cooperation of every single person that lives in Greece.<br />
<br />
/scoff</p>
	
	
	
